                       Extreme Planet! Extreme Planet!
      Explore the hostile conditions on Mars and compare them to Earth.
                   Follow the Water... Follow the Water...
   Be a detective and learn how scientists are looking for signs of water
                                  on Mars.
                           Mars Rocks! Mars Rocks!
       Read about how rocks can tell stories about a planet's history.
                         Life on Mars? Life on Mars?
    Learn what life's all about, and consider how life on another planet
                                 might look.
                  The Martian Mystique The Martian Mystique
    Humans have created all kinds of stories about the Red Planet--check
                        out movies, books, and more.
